{"title":"耳机的正确食用方式","uid":"5f08fd5ad48c212cc4a8dc848484c06e","slug":"耳机的正确食用方式","date":"2020-03-16T02:43:14.000Z","updated":"2022-12-30T16:44:46.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/耳机的正确食用方式.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>*<strong>本文多图警告*</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<p>学校开始上网课了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/kKf9gczWGj47Zms.jpg\"></p>\n<p>为了<strong>听</strong>（更）<strong>清</strong>（好）<strong>讲</strong>（地）<strong>课</strong>（摸）<strong>声</strong>（鱼），我拿出了万年不用的 EarPods。</p>\n<p>它脏得不堪入目，就不放图了。</p>\n<p>用酒精棉片消毒后，戴上，插好，按下 F8。</p>\n<p>一阵阵优美动听的伴奏传入耳朵。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/42TGXQhPbN6viKZ.jpg\"></p>\n<p>拔，插，拔，插，拔，插……</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/8zdqUnhrMuJRxTp.png\"></p>\n<p>等到我终于没有力气了，再次按下 F8。</p>\n<p>一阵阵优美动听的伴奏传入耳朵。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/XgkQjKbN6lih1UE.jpg\"></p>\n<p>身为伪技术人员，这时候当然是去谷歌上<del>借酒消愁找人倾诉</del>寻找正确的解决方法。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>我国的国家标准《GB14471-2013 头戴耳机通用规范》中规定了耳机使用 OMTP 标准，而世界主流的耳机标准是 CTIA。</p>\n<p>它们分别长这样：<img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/3atLw5k6yTAhnHu.jpg\"></p></blockquote>\n<p>这就巧了。我的 MBP 是水货，使用 CTIA 标准，而我买手机送的 EarPods 使用的是 OMTP 标准。</p>\n<p>然后我就打开了某宝，买了它：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/sHkE2gB9qiSGUFA.jpg\"></p>\n<p>虽然它花了 16 天从杭州运到萧山，最后还是换顺丰才拿到快递。</p>\n<p>拿到快递后我异常激动，迫不及待地戴上耳机。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/tIL8DYH4nFRWcp9.jpg\"></p>\n<p>为什么***电流声**这么大！！！而且还时有时无？</p>\n<p>当我打开 QQ，找到一个能发泄愤怒的人想一吐怒气，却发现电流声又没了。我无比满足地把手从键盘上拿开。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/Gl7faJchuEOvXM3.gif\"></p>\n<p>如同嘲讽一般的电流声再次出现了。</p>\n<p>打开 QQ，找到……又没了。</p>\n<p>我无比满……又有了！</p>\n<p>打开 QQ，找到……又没了。</p>\n<p>我无比满……又有了！</p>\n<p>上，下，上，下，上，下……</p>\n<p>******这是为什么啊！！！</p>\n<p>我再次打开了谷歌。</p>\n<p>原来是地线。</p>\n<p>好的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/8zO1H6bLAjPiQJR.gif\"></p>\n<p>MBP 哪里来的地线咯，要有地线的话也不会有国行的两脚充电器咯。</p>\n<p>饱受杂音折磨的日子持续了半天，因为我找到了它：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/VoHTXaylYK4reMc.jpg\" alt=\"为了中考英语听力买的 USB-A 转耳麦双口线\"></p>\n<p>然而这个转接线也是 CTIA 标准的，于是就成了这样：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/yIBqMRF5NZaQdk6.jpg\"></p>\n<p>虽然带了两层放大器，拥有<strong>传统·耳机当音响用·艺能</strong>，音质也停留在“听个响”层面，但能用就行了呀！！！要什么摩托车！！！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dmnbme/blogfiles/main/images/DhkgBYapFJireoR.jpg\"></p>\n","text":"*本文多图警告* 学校开始上网课了。 为了听（更）清（好）讲（地）课（摸）声（鱼），我拿出了万年不用的 EarPods。 它脏得不堪入目，就不放图了。 用酒精棉片消毒后，戴上，插好，按下 F8。 一阵阵优美动听的伴奏传入耳朵。 拔，插，拔，插，拔，插…… 等到我终于没有力气了，再...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":763,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"其他","slug":"其他","count":2,"path":"api/categories/其他.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"耳机","slug":"耳机","count":1,"path":"api/tags/耳机.json"},{"name":"闲","slug":"闲","count":1,"path":"api/tags/闲.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Mai","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"理想主义者、完美主义者、自由主义者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"网速翻倍 爽～～","uid":"846e328e6570c2c620d7b6f63157c6c3","slug":"网速翻倍 爽～～","date":"2020-03-16T02:46:59.000Z","updated":"2022-12-30T17:00:23.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/网速翻倍 爽～～.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"放寒假的那天，一进家门，坐到电脑前突然发现以太网被断掉了（之前路由器就在电脑边上，电脑直连路由器 LAN 口）。转头望向路由器，望了个寂寞。 …… 路！由！器！呢！！！ 走出书房，360 路由器如同庆丰（大雾）溥仪大帝（铺垫）一般在空调上艰难地做着靠背，而舒坦地躺在路由器上的电信...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":773,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Mai","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"理想主义者、完美主义者、自由主义者","socials":{"github":"","twitter"